name: STARTA DOMAIN NAMES (DID)
description:
Create **Decentralized Websites** with **NFT domain names**.
**NFT domains are owned and not leased.**

The domain is **stored in your wallet** and managed **only by you**. Buy the domain with a **one-time registration fee** and never worry about renewals again. **No renewal fees ever**.

Also use as **decentralized digital identities** for the world.

It is in the development process and the whitelist is not defined yet.
